  <section id="cakes" class="top-content">

<h1>Cakes</h1>
</div>
<h1>CELEBRATE YOUR MILESTONES WITH US</h1>
<h2>Here at the Joe's High Rise Bakery, cakes aren't just cakes.  It's a milestone birthday, graduation, a wedding celebration.  We don't take your brightest moments lightly<br>
